    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 3.0",
    "body" : "<p>You need to run it using bash executable like this:</p>\n\n<pre><code>Runtime.getRuntime().exec(\"/bin/bash -c **YouTerminalSoftWareName**\");\n</code></pre>\n\n<p>YouTerminalSoftWareName must be absolute path or aready in your PATH environment variable</p>\n"
